Events','no'),(261,'_ministry_6_events_heading','field_537ac1a185840','no'),(262,'ministry_6_vibe_banner','','no'),(263,'_ministry_6_vibe_banner','field_535d47ac31b0e','no'),(266,'ministry_11_events_heading','Men\'s Events','no'),(267,'_ministry_11_events_heading','field_537ac1a185840','no'),(268,'ministry_11_tile_image','693','no'),(269,'_ministry_11_tile_image','field_539949c5a6b52','no'),(270,'ministry_11_vibe_banner','','no'),(271,'_ministry_11_vibe_banner','field_535d47ac31b0e','no'),(278,'teaching_series_8_foreground','white','no'),(279,'_teaching_series_8_foreground','field_53845d1e64fa9','no'),(284,'post_count','2','yes'),(289,'ministry_12_events_heading','Events','no'),(290,'_ministry_12_events_heading','field_537ac1a185840','no'),(291,'ministry_12_tile_image','1277','no'),(292,'_ministry_12_tile_image','field_539949c5a6b52','no'),(293,'ministry_12_vibe_banner','','no'),(294,'_ministry_12_vibe_banner','field_535d47ac31b0e','no'),(313,'ministry_11_content','We believe that men who are disciples of Jesus are brothers. Bridgetown Men works to build Godly friendships that will enable men to grow as leaders in their home, church, business, community, recreation and wherever else God takes them.\r\n<h4>423 Men</h4>\r\nBridgetown wants to help men break the addictive cycle of sexual sin. Private groups of men gather weekly to honestly discuss sexuality and pray for purity. [email address=423men@ajesuschurch.org]Contact us confidentially[/email] to be placed in a group.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','no'),(314,'_ministry_11_content','field_53900b9fae549','no'),(316,'ministry_3_content','At Bridgetown, we love kids. We want to provide a fun and safe environment for kids to learn about Jesus. We want our classrooms to be marked by learning and laughter. We want our events to be full of energy and excitement. We want our parents to be well equipped and supported. We want our kids to encounter Jesus and become his disciples. Because that\'s what it\'s all about. If you are interested in learning more about Bridgetown Kids, someone from our kids staff would love to chat with you. [page_actions] [email address=bridgetownkids@ajesuschurch.org]Connect With Us[/email][/page_actions]\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><b>Kids Sunday Gathering</b></h1>\r\nBridgetown Kids is for Ages 0 – Grade 5. We meet Sundays during the 5 PM church gathering, providing a fun and safe place for kids to learn about Jesus. We are located downstairs, beneath the annex. Kids drop-off begins at 4:45 PM. Parking for families with kids is provided at SW 12th &amp; Salmon St. and is offered for free with a Family Parking Pass. To receive a Family Parking Pass please speak to a kids worker.\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222;\">We keep Bridgetown Kids organized and running smoothly by using an online registration tool called KidCheck during drop-off and pick-up. Registration on KidCheck is safe, secure, and free and it only takes a few minutes.</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222;\">[page_actions]<a href=\"https://go.kidcheck.com/signin.aspx?action=register\" target=\"_blank\">Register For KidCheck </a>[/page_actions]</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222;\">\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #222222;\">Kids Parties</h1>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222;\">[two_third padding=\"0 25px 0 0\"]We want to reward kids for Jesus-like behavior in a way that does not promote consumerism. Rather than rewarding our kids with the opportunity to get more toys and candy, we are going to turn it into a classroom event! Every few months, kids in grades 1 – 5 will hang out and have a ton of fun! We will eat pizza, play games, and watch a movie. We would love for your kids to come and to bring their friends!</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222;\">[/two_third][one_third_last]</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222;\">\r\n<div><strong>Dates:</strong> May 6, Aug 26, Oct 28</div>\r\n<div><strong>Time: </strong>6:30 – 9 PM</div>\r\n<div><strong>Location:</strong> Bridgetown Office, 1306 NW Hoyt Street, Unit 412 Portland, OR 97209</div>\r\n<div><strong>Cost:</strong> None</div>\r\n<div>[/one_third_last]</div>\r\n<div>[page_actions]<a href=\"http://bridgetown.wpengine.com/kids-party-registration/\">Register For Kids Party</a> [email address=justin@ajesuschurch.org]Contact For More Information[/email][/page_actions]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222;\">\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222;\">\r\n<h2>Become a Kids Leader</h2>\r\nBridgetown Kids is fueled by the efforts of our amazing volunteer leaders and we are always looking to grow our team! If you are interested in serving kids at Bridgetown, we would love to hear from you. Attend our next Kids Orientation to learn more about becoming a kids leader. All kids leaders must pass certain prerequisites including a background check.\r\n<div>[page_actions] [email address=bridgetownkids@ajesuschurch.org]Contact For More Information[/email][/page_actions]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222;\">\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n</div>','no'),(317,'_ministry_3_content','field_53900b9fae549','no'),(318,'ministry_3_events_heading','Kids Events','no'),(319,'_ministry_3_events_heading','field_537ac1a185840','no'),(320,'ministry_3_tile_image','695','no'),(321,'_ministry_3_tile_image','field_539949c5a6b52','no'),(322,'ministry_3_vibe_banner','','no'),(323,'_ministry_3_vibe_banner','field_535d47ac31b0e','no'),(329,'ministry_6_content','Bridgetown Young Adults (18–26) purposes with transitioning young adults into the life of the church as self-giving, mature adults actively participating in the mission of God.','no'),(330,'_ministry_6_content','field_53900b9fae549','no'),(332,'ministry_12_content','Bridgetown Women works to build Godly friendships which are centered around vibrant and authentic fellowship with Jesus. Through prayer, studying the Scriptures, and time together, we hope to better learn what it means to be a woman who follows Jesus. We regularly host different events for women in all stages of life to gather together. Look forward to different opportunities happening regularly.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #333333;\">423 Women</span></strong></h1>\r\nWe are a group of women; broken, redeemed, Jesus followers, committed to the process of allowing Holy Spirit to heal us and bring freedom from our present struggle with sexual issues or behavior and addiction. We do this by stepping into the light, confessing our sins, and the sins committed against us in a safe, confidential environment. We are not a recovery group, rather a group committed to asking and allowing Jesus to transform our sexuality that has been broken by our own sexual choices and addictive behavior, the lies Satan has told us about ourselves, and from the culture we live in that has contributed to our wrong thinking about our identity.\r\n<div>We meet for 9 months, once a week in small groups, keeping each other accountable and working through a curriculum that is designed to reveal the root of our struggle and lead us to the feet of Jesus. Contact us confidentlly to meet with a 423 Women leader.</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #222222;\">[page_actions][email address=423women@ajesuschurch.org]Confidential Contact[/email][/page_actions]</span>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n</div>','no'),(333,'_ministry_12_content','field_53900b9fae549','no'),(341,'ministry_11_foreground','white','no'),(342,'_ministry_11_foreground','field_537f17c949914','no'),(343,'ministry_11_hero_graphic','1210','no'),(344,'_ministry_11_hero_graphic','field_535d48d19a78d','no'),(345,'ministry_11_hero_phrase','','no'),(346,'_ministry_11_hero_phrase','field_535f146b1c2b1','no'),(347,'ministry_11_vimeo_id','','no'),(348,'_ministry_11_vimeo_id','field_535d4fb339065','no'),(349,'ministry_11_watch