container\'><iframe src=\'https://www.youtube.com/embed//OVRixfameGY\' frameborder=\'0\' allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n\n<h5>More Available Soon from <a href=\"https://jointhebibleproject.com/?\" target=\"_blank\">The Bible Project</a></h5>','Book Videos','','inherit','open','open','','1729-autosave-v1','','','2016-06-15 14:34:52','2016-06-15 22:34:52','',1729,'http://bridgetown.wpengine.com/1729-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1742,4,'2015-12-30 16:19:50','2015-12-31 00:19:50','','ajc_bt_yobl_thumb_themevideo','','inherit','open','open','','ajc_bt_yobl_thumb_themevideo','','','2015-12-30 16:19:50','2015-12-31 00:19:50','',1734,'http://bridgetown.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2015/12/ajc_bt_yobl_thumb_themevideo.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1745,22,'2015-10-20 16:45:35','2015-10-20 23:45:35','The current refugee crisis has forced millions of people around the world to flee their homes, and the number grows daily. The quota for refugees entering the United States started over on October 1, so there will be around 1,300 refugees coming to Portland within the next year.\r\n\r\nRefugee families arrive to the U.S., usually with just a garbage bag of clothes or a couple suitcases. They’re set up in a small apartment, but they lack all of the household items needed to begin their lives again. Restart Kits provide these items that are desperately needed upon arrival.\r\n\r\nRestart Kits are a tangible way of showing God’s love to people that have faced devastating circumstances. We want refugees to know that they’re welcome here, and that we\'re excited and honored to have them in Portland.\r\n\r\nThere are six different types of Restart Kits: personal care kit, kitchen kit, bathroom kit, cleaning kit, baby kit, and a welcome kit, which include toiletries, dishes and silverware, bath towels, laundry detergent, baby diapers, and other essential items.\r\n\r\n[page_actions]<a href=\"http://www.hearthecry.org/site/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Restart.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Restart Kit Item Lists</a> [/page_actions]\r\n<h1>Refugee Care Collection Day</h1>\r\n<strong>Saturday, Oct 24, between 12 – 5 PM</strong>\r\n<strong>10160 SW Nimbus Ave, Suite F-3, Portland, OR, 97223</strong>\r\n\r\nWe’re collecting Restart Kits and new or gently used winter jackets during the Refugee Care Collection Day. There’s a huge need with hundreds of refugees coming to Portland in the next few months. So the invitation is to look at the Refugee Restart Kit List, and build a Restart Kit or bring a couple winter jackets. Thanks for helping us welcome refugees to Portland!\r\n\r\n[page_actions][email address=Megan@HearTheCry.org]Contact for more information[/email][/page_actions]\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1746\" src=\"http://bridgetown.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/ajc_blog_refugee_1.jpg\" alt=\"ajc_blog_refugee_1\" width=\"1200\" height=\"691\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1747\" src=\"http://bridgetown.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/ajc_blog_refugeee_2_.jpg\" alt=\"ajc_blog_refugeee_2_\" width=\"1200\" height=\"691\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1748\" src=\"http://bridgetown.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/ajc_blog_refugeee_3.jpg\" alt=\"ajc_blog_refugeee_3\" width=\"1200\" height=\"691\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1749\" src=\"http://bridgetown.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/ajc_blog_refugeee_4.jpg\" alt=\"ajc_blog_refugeee_4\" width=\"1200\" height=\"691\" />','Care for Refugees in Portland','','publish','closed','closed','','care-for-refugees','','','2016-07-18 23:30:15','2016-07-19 07:30:15','',0,'http://bridgetown.wpengine.com/?p=1745',0,'post','',0),(1751,4,'2015-12-30 16:38:40','2015-12-31 00:38:40','','ajc_bt_yobl_hero_bookvideos','','inherit','open','open','','ajc_bt_yobl_hero_bookvideos','','','2015-12-30 16:38:40','2015-12-31 00:38:40','',1729,'http://bridgetown.wpengine.co